20-01-28T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"有口罩的home office<br />\n無口罩的返 office"},{"pid":"ff19d4ce8ee7a3b827cde12450ab8a2c050b52a3","tid":1848460,"uid":132676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔返工=唔洗出街=唔洗口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd84da83ec9cf70ac7f522f741cad288199f9a3e","tid":1848460,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa4aba6025cced18bd67304c1e894be2be72d851","tid":1848460,"uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18e23633f21a2fdb72de7f8b0808d64320dce783","tid":1848460,"uid":304663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"屌，咁搞法真係一罐餐肉，汁一劑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"有口罩的home office<br />\n無口罩的返 office"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"情願係病毒來自實驗室，咁姐係有解藥。"},{"pid":"39bf1bbeca23c29070830ca9e951c9a826e87e2f","tid":1848460,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bed9b5b344f866d4e9bbb4b44fb0a1701d22a36e","tid":1848460,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=ddbf5ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n護目鏡：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=e727f659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=1fc047e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=425b8105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=5d6c198c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=dfb1bf43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=9a2945e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液"},{"pid":"26b3235ff2e1428a01d420a4062b5075d39f1500","tid":1848460,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:02:57.000Z","msg":"開佢公司名"},{"pid":"f7d794937389791137fef7719110f7f74e3b1522","tid":1848460,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25465ff5c1d6df6b526231c81f6b67230ab3228f","tid":1848460,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"仲請唔請人，想攞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"攞完即刻辭職"},{"pid":"32982d6cc7586cee65266a0b03e94a2f87706149","tid":1848460,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8d3972a85c6f5d636a9923e4df2bf6eb200b81","tid":1848460,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"謝主隆恩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"不過諗落都算係咁，又無迫人返office<br />\n要返既話又有口罩比返你，保障返其他人，好過叫你返但又無罩既公司"},{"pid":"65c94e7585cdefd92f47fa44230c1676ef811c20","tid":1848460,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"好撚大恩大德喎"},{"pid":"6e518d67177b4a7654b92a3172addcdf05a24ddb","tid":1848460,"uid":114875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]